===[[Pokémon Masters EX]]===
{{main|Shauna (Masters)}}
Shauna forms a [[sync pair]] with {{p|Chesnaught}}, {{p|Klefki}}, {{p|Delcatty}}, and {{p|Sylveon}} in [[Pokémon Masters EX]]. Shauna became a playable sync pair on January 16, 2023.

Shauna first appeared as an NPC during the [[Kalos]] chapter of the [[villain arc]].

